<p><b>What are the 4 market strategies of Kotler?</b> Philip Kotler introduced what is commonly known as the 4Ps of marketing: product, price, place and promotion. The '4Ps', or the marketing mix, is a description of the strategic position of a product in the marketplace.</p>
